# S05-T10: Board (live kanban) + Activity Timeline

## Objective
Visualize agents working in realtime (taskboard-supabase feel) + an activity timeline.

## Execution
- Board view per accepted epic: kanban columns todo/in_progress/done, fed by `wc_tasks`
  and live-patched from `useRealtime()` (T09) — cards move on `task.moved` without refresh.
- Per-task: lead-role badge, agent state, a "Run" button (calls T08; disabled while gate LOCKED,
  with an "Open gate" affordance that calls T08's open-gate).
- Activity timeline panel: ordered `wc_activity` + live `agent.activity` events (actor type
  human|agent). This is the timeline-lite seed; the time-machine scrubber is S07.
- Reuse glass UI + existing `WorkTaskColumn`/`WorkTaskCard` where possible.

## Out
`apps/work-control/app/components/{BoardView,ActivityTimeline}.vue`, board page

## Done when
- Running a task animates live across columns; timeline streams agent events in order.
